        "i18n_job_wnt_desc": "<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.weenat.com\">www.weenat.com</a> | 5 to 15 employees | Nantes, FRANCE <br> Weenat allows the farmers to optimize their resources, by bringing them localized information in the plot to support their decisions.",
        "i18n_job_wnt_date": "Jan 2016 - Oct 2017",
        "i18n_job_wnt_title1": "Projects Manager",
        "i18n_job_wnt_text1": "In this small and young company, I had many responsibilities. My four main missions:",
        "i18n_job_wnt_mission1": "Create, developp and improve agronomic models and Decision Support Tools (DST)<span class=\"font-icon-plus\"></span><span class=\"font-icon-minus\"></span>",
        "i18n_job_wnt_proj1": "My main mission was to supervise creation and improvement of agronomic models and Decision Support Tools (DST) based on data (rain, humidity, temperature, soil tensiometry and temperature, ...) from sensors into the fields. The aim was to give farmers or researchers tools to confirm their decisions. As a Product Manager, I managed these projects from A to Z through: <br> - identifying users' needs and expectations <br> - structuring the model or calculations and data analyses <br> - leading the different trades involved (electronics, development) or teams from other companies <br> - implementing tests to confirm the interest of the DSTs <br> - placing the product on the market with commercial team. <br>Ten DST projects were successfully completed on various topics (irrigation, pests, fertilization, crop protection products, monitoring of growth and development).",
        "i18n_job_wnt_mission2": "Research and development of new strategic partnerships <span class=\"font-icon-plus\"></span><span class=\"font-icon-minus\"></span>",
        "i18n_job_wnt_proj2": "I've participated to congresses and colloquies to meet people of the agricultural sector who could work with Weenat on innovation projects. Two innovative projects I contributed to launch: <br> - Detecting and manage nitrogen doses in the field thanks to new sensors and models <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;o Weenat’s selected project is mounted with National Agricultural Research Institute and Chambers of Agriculture (consular organization for farming development) <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;o The call for projects programme is “Innovative initiatives in agriculture and agri-food” launched by French Ministry of Agriculture. <br> - Developing a DST to apply a biocontrol product under optimum conditions <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;o Weenat’s partners are a cooperative, researchers and an agro-chemical industrial <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;o The call for projects programme is the “Single Interdepartmental Fund” housed within the French Ministry of Economy, Industry and Employment.",
        "i18n_job_wnt_mission3": "Key account management<span class=\"font-icon-plus\"></span><span class=\"font-icon-minus\"></span>",
        "i18n_job_wnt_proj3": "I was responsible of key accounts management by: <br> - Editing quotes, tracking orders and shipments <br> - Assisting installation on site <br> - Caring customers before, during and after the production season <br> - Analysing the feedbacks and transfer it to the person concerned (informatic,electronic, ...) <br> - Brainstorming ways that we might be able to respond to their issues and start newproject if needed",
        "i18n_job_wnt_proj4": "I also worked on communication and marketing topics by: <br> - Following the news about agricultural community, technologies, competitors, etc. <br> - Sharing news about the company and agri-tech sector innovations on social networks (twitter, facebook, website) <br> - Participating in fairs and events, like Paris International Agricultural Show (SIA), Paris International Agribusiness Show (SIMA), ... <br> - Contributing to communication media design from being Product Manager",
        "i18n_job_wnt_mission4": "Communication and marketing<span class=\"font-icon-plus\"></span><span class=\"font-icon-minus\"></span>",
        "i18n_job_wnt_cate": "Pro",
        "i18n_job_wnt_them": "#agri #tech",
        "i18n_job_wnt_sum": "In this startup combining technology and agronomy, I was in charge of the Decision Support Tools and some key accounts.",

        "i18n_job_pio_cate": "Pro",
        "i18n_job_pio_them": "#agri",
        "i18n_job_pio_sum": "My main mission was to gather data for the annual technical result book, and I was writing technical arguments for marketing and communication materials.",
        "i18n_job_pio_entr": "Dupont Pioneer",
        "i18n_job_pio_desc": "<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.pioneer.com\">www.pioneer.com</a> | More than 10,000 employees worldwide | Aussonne, FRANCE <br> Dupont Pioneer is an international seed company specialized in maize, sunflower, oilseed rape and soybean.",
        "i18n_job_pio_date1": "May - Dec 2015",
